lab3 /little service with flask python
docker build -t flask-service .
docker run -d -p 5001:5000 flask-service

lab4 / sqlite connected with flask. Logic is to POST and GET data drom DB
docker build -t flask-db-service .
docker run -d -p 5001:5000 flask-db-service
--- Data for posting to db ----
curl -X POST http://localhost:5001/messages \
-H "Content-Type: application/json" \
-d '{"text":"Hello Lab 4"}'